Package mainPackage

Class Summary
ConditionExpression container for a plain-text phrase of a CPG that includes conditions and the corresponding ID of the condition
ConditionTranslator This class gets an annotated gate-Document and filters logic conditions and creates the necessary container condition classes of the package conditions with the found informations.
ConditionWrapper this class holds an instance of the GateController class for handeling the gate features and MetaMap-controller the methods of the GateController are called and the results are written into the output file
GateController the gate controller handels the communication with gate and with metamap, over a plug-in for gate, it instanciates the necessary objects of gate, configures it, annotates input documents, executes them with gate and metamap and holds an instance of the condition-translater, which translates gate-documents into logic conditions
mainClass console application to test the Condition-Wrapper
MetaMapConfiguration this class is a container for metamap configurations.
MetaMapPR This class is the implementation of the resource METAMAP.
 

Enum Summary
ConditionType enumeration containing the different condition types that are known by Asbru
FileNameType defines the type of the read file (input | output | metamap configuration)
